  <scopecontent id="aspace_8345ca253907f91d6e63b75cba8e2ba7">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>The Harold Edwards Notebooks (dated 1971-2021) consists of spiral-bound notebooks containing the travel and research journals of Harold (Hal) Edwards. While the notebooks primarily document the mathematical problems he was working on, they also contain conversations with collaborators and colleagues, observations from his travels, and notes on his writing process.</p>  </scopecontent>
